extends base

block content
    main.main
        section
            h1 About DNS Lookup Tool
            p
                | The DNS Lookup Tool is designed to provide users with an easy-to-use interface to explore DNS records for any domain. 
                | It supports various DNS record types, such as A, AAAA, MX, TXT, CNAME, and more.
            p
                | Whether you're a developer troubleshooting domain configurations or a user looking for more information about a domain, 
                | this tool helps you fetch detailed DNS information with ease.
        section
            h2 Features
            ul
                li Fetch multiple DNS record types like A, AAAA, MX, TXT, and more
                li User-friendly interface for quick lookups
                li Responsive design for desktop and mobile users
                li Supports detailed results for each DNS record type
        section
            h2 How It Works
            p
                | The tool uses Node.js and modern web technologies to query DNS records in real-time. It provides a simple interface to request
                | specific DNS records or perform a full lookup across all available record types. Results are displayed in an organized and readable format.
        section
            h2 Contact Us
            p
                | If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to 
                a(href="/contact") contact us.
